cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper involves computer vision techniques for odometry estimation and metric localisation in radar. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves robotics and autonomous systems, which falls under cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves natural language processing techniques for abstract summarization, which could fall under cs.CL (Computation and Language).
